{
  "text": "Journal of the New Economic Association, 41(1), 159-185. Solntsev, I., [CITATION_1] , Designing a performance measurement framework for regional networks of national sports organizations: Evidence from Russian football. Managing Sport and Leisure, 23(1-2), 7-27. Van Reeth, D., [CITATION_2] , The impact of hosting the 2018 FIFA world cup on differences in TV viewership between seasoned football fans and occasional watchers of football games in Russia. Journal of Sports Economics. DOI: 10.1177/1527002519885421. Zubakin, V.A., Kosorukov, O.A., Moiseev, N.A. (2015) , Improvement of regression forecasting models. Modern Applied Science, 9(6), 344-353.",
